OL,3,CThames Water rescue in doubt as
OL,4,CEnvironment Secretary raises objections
OL,6,FThames Water is reportedly on the
OL,7,Fbrink of temporary nationalisation
OL,8,Fafter the Environment Secretary cast
OL,9,Fdoubt on a #10 billion rescue deal for
OL,10,Fthe troubled supplier.
OL,12,FEnvironment Secretary Emma Reynolds
OL,13,Fhas written to water regulator Ofwat,
OL,14,Fwarning the current bid tabled by
OL,15,FThames Water creditors would place an
OL,16,F"undue burden" on customers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
