CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781671666
OL,3,CThames Water rescue in doubt as
OL,4,CEnvironment Secretary raises objections
OL,6,FThe government's misgivings over the
OL,7,Fdeal comes as Ofwat is said to have
OL,8,Fbeen close to accepting the offer from
OL,9,Fbidding consortium London & Valley
OL,10,FWater, which has proposed injecting
OL,11,F#10 billion into debt-laden Thames
OL,12,FWater in return for any new fines over
OL,13,Fsewage leaks being waived for four
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FSpeaking to broadcasters, Reynolds
OL,17,Fsaid she did not "want Thames Water
OL,18,Fconsumers to pick up the bill for
OL,19,Ftheir failures".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781671666
OL,3,CThames Water rescue in doubt as
OL,4,CEnvironment Secretary raises objections
OL,6,FShe said her letter expressed early
OL,7,Fconcerns about the creditors proposal
OL,8,Fand that they "don't do enough to
OL,9,Fprotect the consumers and the
OL,10,Fenvironment".
OL,12,FReynolds said she had "3 particular
OL,13,Fconcerns" including the delays to the
OL,14,Fimprovement of the environment and
OL,15,Fwater infrastructure as well as "the
OL,16,Funfair cost and burden on the
OL,17,Fconsumers".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
