OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781671666
OL,3,CThames Water rescue in doubt as
OL,4,CEnvironment Secretary raises objections
OL,6,FA spokesperson from Thames Water has
OL,7,Fwelcomed the letter from Reynolds and
OL,8,Fsaid: "It is positive that the
OL,9,FSecretary of State has provided
OL,10,Ffeedback to Ofwat in relation to the
OL,11,FLondon & Valley Water plan.
OL,13,F"We will continue working with all
OL,14,Fparties to reach an agreement that
OL,15,Fsupports long-term financial stability
OL,16,Fand delivers better outcomes for
OL,17,Fcustomers and the environment."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
