OL,3,CThames Water rescue in doubt as
OL,4,CEnvironment Secretary raises objections
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThames Water is Britain's biggest
OL,12,Fwater supplier with 16 million
OL,13,Fcustomers and is hoping to secure the
OL,14,Fdeal to avoid temporary
OL,15,Fnationalisation after being left close
OL,16,Fto collapse with nearly #20 billion of
OL,17,Fdebt.
OL,19,FIt has also faced a series of hefty
OL,20,Ffines for its poor environmental
OL,21,Fperformance in recent years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
