PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781671666
OL,3,CThames Water rescue in doubt as
OL,4,CEnvironment Secretary raises objections
OL,6,FA rescue bid by creditors is seen as
OL,7,Fthe final realistic option on the
OL,8,Ftable to avoid being placed into the
OL,9,Fgovernment's so-called special
OL,10,Fadministration regime after a previous
OL,11,Frescue deal with US private equity
OL,12,Fgiant KKR collapsed in May last year.
OL,14,FReynolds's criticism of the deal
OL,15,Fcentres on concerns that customers
OL,16,Fwill lose out under the creditors'
OL,17,Foffer and called the proposal "weak".
OL,19,FBut the government has repeatedly said
OL,20,Fit prefers a "market solution" over
OL,21,Ftemporary nationalisation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
