PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781671666
OL,3,CThames Water rescue in doubt as
OL,4,CEnvironment Secretary raises objections
OL,6,FThames Water also supports a "market-
OL,7,Fled solution" claiming it will "ensure
OL,8,Fthe uninterrupted delivery of our
OL,9,Fbiggest infrastructure upgrade in 150
OL,10,Fyears".
OL,12,FThe government had been expected to
OL,13,Fback the takeover, with the utility
OL,14,Ffast running out of cash and said to
OL,15,Fbe facing collapse within months if a
OL,16,Fdeal is not forthcoming.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
