OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781671666
OL,3,CThames Water rescue in doubt as
OL,4,CEnvironment Secretary raises objections
OL,6,FLabour Leadership hopeful, Andy
OL,7,FBurnham, who is hoping to win the
OL,8,FMakerfield by-election on Thursday as
OL,9,Fhis first step towards the challenge,
OL,10,Frecently proposed a 10-year plan to
OL,11,Frenationalise the water industry.
OL,13,FLondon & Valley Water's proposed deal
OL,14,Fwould see it inject #3.35 billion of
OL,15,Fnew equity into Thames Water and up to
OL,16,F#6.55 billion in new debt.
OL,18,FBut it is said that Thames Water would
OL,19,Falso have to pay nearly #750 million
OL,20,Fto its creditors, lawyers and advisers
OL,21,Fas part of the restructuring.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
