OL,3,CThames Water rescue in doubt as
OL,4,CEnvironment Secretary raises objections
OL,6,FThe supplier would reportedly still
OL,7,Fowe #160 million in fees, plus #285
OL,8,Fmillion in accrued interest to
OL,9,Fcreditors, including institutional
OL,10,Finvestors such as US hedge funds
OL,11,FElliott Management and Silverpoint
OL,12,FCapital.
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
